ZH: 他总是避实就虚，从不直接回答问题。
EN: He always beats around the bush and never gives a direct answer.

ZH: 别再避实就虚了，告诉我实话吧！
EN: Stop dodging the issue and tell me the truth!

ZH: 她不喜欢避实就虚，直来直去的说话。
EN: She doesn't like beating around the bush and prefers to speak straightforwardly.

ZH: 老板很会避实就虚，不让员工知道真相。
EN: The boss is good at being evasive and doesn't let the employees know the truth.

ZH: 在谈判中，他总是避实就虚，让对方摸不着头脑。
EN: In negotiations, he always dodges the issue and leaves the other party confused.

ZH: 这位政客擅长避实就虚，让人看不清他的真实意图。
EN: This politician is adept at being evasive and making it hard for people to see his true intentions.

ZH: 如果你一直避实就虚，那么我们之间的信任就会受到影响。
EN: If you keep beating around the bush, our trust will be affected.

ZH: 他的回答总是避实就虚，让人觉得他在隐瞒什么。
EN: His answers are always evasive, making people think he is hiding something.

ZH: 她遇到困难时常常避实就虚，不愿意向别人寻求帮助。
EN: When she faces difficulties, she tends to be evasive and doesn't want to seek help from others.

ZH: 下次请别再避实就虚，说清楚自己的立场。
EN: Next time, please don't dodge the issue and make clear your position.

ZH: 他总是避实就虚，像是在逃避责任。
EN: He always beats around the bush, as if avoiding responsibility.

ZH: 这个演讲太过避实就虚了，没有说到重点。
EN: This speech was too evasive and didn't get to the main point.

ZH: 他的问题回答总是避实就虚，让人无法得到真实信息。
EN: His answers to questions are always evasive, making it hard to get real information.

ZH: 老板对员工的问题总是避实就虚，不愿意透露真实情况。
EN: The boss always dodges the issues raised by employees and is not willing to reveal the real situation.

ZH: 她总是避实就虚，从不坦率表达自己的想法。
EN: She always beats around the bush and never expresses her true thoughts openly.

ZH: 我们需要直截了当地对待问题，而不是避实就虚。
EN: We need to deal with the issues directly instead of being evasive.

ZH: 他在工作上避实就虚，不敢直面自己的错误。
EN: He is evasive in his job and dares not face his own mistakes.

ZH: 不要避实就虚，坦诚面对困难。
EN: Don't beat around the bush, face difficulties candidly.

ZH: 老师总是避实就虚，不愿意直接批评学生错误。
EN: The teacher always dodges the issue and is not willing to criticize students' mistakes directly.

ZH: 这个政策避实就虚，没有解决实际问题。
EN: This policy is evasive and does not solve the actual problems.
